name: WE.
description:
This limited series collection of images captures actress Katie Cassidy embracing the art of self-love with the intention of empowering women and inspiring them to love themselves. Shot during Women’s History Month by celebrity photographers Drew and Derek Riker, Cassidy utilizes a Love is Art cotton canvas along with black and white paint on her body to showcase her desire for women to appreciate, advocate and celebrate themselves.

Portions of proceeds will benefit The Rape Foundation, Women’s Global Empowerment Fund and LifeWay Network.
